Package org.apache.bcel.classfile

Class StackMap

java.lang.Object
org.apache.bcel.classfile.Attribute
org.apache.bcel.classfile.StackMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, Node
public final class StackMap extends Attribute
This class represents a stack map attribute used for preverification of Java classes for the Java 2 Micro Edition (J2ME). This attribute is used by the KVM and contained within the Code attribute of a method. See CLDC specification ï¿½5.3.1.2 
 StackMapTable_attribute {
   u2              attribute_name_index;
   u4              attribute_length;
   u2              number_of_entries;
   stack_map_frame entries[number_of_entries];
 }
